## 6️⃣ **Automazione CI/CD per Nexus**  

```yaml
# .github/workflows/nexus.yml
name: Nexus CI
on:
  push:
    branches: [ main ]
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu‑latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Build eBPF filter
        run: |
          clang -O2 -target bpf -c filter_la_sig.c -o filter_la_sig.o
      - name: Docker image
        run: |
          docker build -t nexus-node:${{ github.sha }} .
      - name: Deploy to fleet
        uses: appleboy/ssh-action@v0.1.10
        with:
          host: ${{ secrets.FLEET_HOST }}
          username: ${{ secrets.FLEET_USER }}
          key: ${{ secrets.FLEET_SSH }}
          script: |
            docker pull nexus-node:${{ github.sha }}
            docker run -d --restart unless‑stopped \
              --net host \
              -v /etc/nexus:/etc/nexus \
              nexus-node:${{ github.sha }}
```

*Il workflow garantisce che **ogni commit** includa la versione più recente del filtro LA‑SIG, del gestore di clock e del ciclo di auto‑guarigione.*  

